00365                                           MACRO SET_INT_VECTOR
00366                                             push ds
00367                                             xor ax, ax
00368                                             mov ds, ax
00369                                             mov ax, ?3
00370                                             mov ?1*4, ax
00371                                             mov ax, ?2
00372                                             mov ?1*4+2, ax
00373                                             pop ds
00374                                           MEND

00445                       00000128            vgabios_init_func:
00446                                           ;; init vga card
00447 0128           E8         3472              call init_vga_card
00448                                           ;; init basic bios vars
00449 012B           E8         34CE              call init_bios_area
00450                                           ;; init vbe functions
00451 012E           E8         9854              call vbe_init
00452                                           ;; set int10 vect
00453                                             SET_INT_VECTOR(0x10, #0xC000, #vgabios_int10_handler)
 +a   0131           1E                           push ds
 +a   0132           31C0                         xor ax, ax
 +a   0134           8ED8                         mov ds, ax
 +a   0136           B8                   0152    mov ax,  #vgabios_int10_handler
 +a   0139           A3         0040              mov 0x10*4, ax
 +a   013C           B8                   C000    mov ax,  #0xC000
 +a   013F           A3         0042              mov 0x10*4+2, ax
 +a   0142           1F                           pop ds
00454                                           ;; display splash screen
00455 0143           E8         350A              call _display_splash_screen
00456                                           ;; init video mode and clear the screen
00457 0146           B8                   0003    mov ax,#0x0003
00458 0149           CD                     10    int #0x10
00459                                           ;; show info
00460 014B           E8         3503              call _display_info
00461                                           ;; show vbe info
00462 014E           E8         9862              call vbe_display_info
00463 0151           CB                           retf
00464                                           ! 282 endasm
00465                                           !BCC_ENDASM
00466                                           ! 283 #asm
00467                                           !BCC_ASM
00468                       00000152            vgabios_int10_handler:
00469 0152           9C                           pushf
00470 0153           80FC                   0F    cmp ah, #0x0f
00471 0156           75           06              jne int10_test_1A
00472 0158           E8         6105              call biosfn_get_video_mode
00473 015B           E9         00C5              jmp int10_end
00474                       0000015E            int10_test_1A:
00475 015E           80FC                   1A    cmp ah, #0x1a
00476 0161           75           06              jne int10_test_0B
00477 0163           E8         6E91              call biosfn_group_1A
00478 0166           E9         00BA              jmp int10_end
00479                       00000169            int10_test_0B:
00480 0169           80FC                   0B    cmp ah, #0x0b
00481 016C           75           06              jne int10_test_1103
00482 016E           E8         581E              call biosfn_group_0B
00483 0171           E9         00AF              jmp int10_end
00484                       00000174            int10_test_1103:
00485 0174           3D                   1103    cmp ax, #0x1103
00486 0177           75           06              jne int10_test_12
00487 0179           E8         67DF              call biosfn_set_text_block_specifier
00488 017C           E9         00A4              jmp int10_end
00489                       0000017F            int10_test_12:
00490 017F           80FC                   12    cmp ah, #0x12
00491 0182           75           3E              jne int10_test_101B
00492 0184           80FB                   10    cmp bl, #0x10
00493 0187           75           06              jne int10_test_BL30
00494 0189           E8         6C93              call biosfn_get_ega_info
00495 018C           E9         0094              jmp int10_end
00496                       0000018F            int10_test_BL30:
00497 018F           80FB                   30    cmp bl, #0x30
00498 0192           75           06              jne int10_test_BL31
00499 0194           E8         6CAC              call biosfn_select_vert_res
00500 0197           E9         0089              jmp int10_end
00501                       0000019A            int10_test_BL31:
00502 019A           80FB                   31    cmp bl, #0x31
00503 019D           75           05              jne int10_test_BL32
00504 019F           E8         6CF4              call biosfn_enable_default_palette_loading
00505 01A2           EB           7F              jmp int10_end
00506                       000001A4            int10_test_BL32:
00507 01A4           80FB                   32    cmp bl, #0x32
00508 01A7           75           05              jne int10_test_BL33
00509 01A9           E8         6D0C              call biosfn_enable_video_addressing
00510 01AC           EB           75              jmp int10_end
00511                       000001AE            int10_test_BL33:
00512 01AE           80FB                   33    cmp bl, #0x33
00513 01B1           75           05              jne int10_test_BL34
00514 01B3           E8         6D20              call biosfn_enable_grayscale_summing
00515 01B6           EB           6B              jmp int10_end
00516                       000001B8            int10_test_BL34:
00517 01B8           80FB                   34    cmp bl, #0x34
00518 01BB           75           58              jne int10_normal
00519 01BD           E8         6D3A              call biosfn_enable_cursor_emulation
00520 01C0           EB           61              jmp int10_end
00521                       000001C2            int10_test_101B:
00522 01C2           3D                   101B    cmp ax, #0x101b
00523 01C5           74           4E              je int10_normal
00524 01C7           80FC                   10    cmp ah, #0x10
00525 01CA           75           05              jne int10_test_4F
00526 01CC           E8         60B8              call biosfn_group_10
00527 01CF           EB           52              jmp int10_end
00528                       000001D1            int10_test_4F:
00529 01D1           80FC                   4F    cmp ah, #0x4f
00530 01D4           75           3F              jne int10_normal
00531 01D6           3C                     03    cmp al, #0x03
00532 01D8           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_05
00533 01DA           E8         9CDB              call vbe_biosfn_return_current_mode
00534 01DD           EB           44              jmp int10_end
00535                       000001DF            int10_test_vbe_05:
00536 01DF           3C                     05    cmp al, #0x05
00537 01E1           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_06
00538 01E3           E8         9FA6              call vbe_biosfn_display_window_control
00539 01E6           EB           3B              jmp int10_end
00540                       000001E8            int10_test_vbe_06:

00542 01EA           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_07

00544 01EF           EB           32              jmp int10_end

00563 0210           E8         A0F2              call vbe_biosfn_display_identification_extensions

00567 0216           1E                           push ds

00571 021B           8EDB                         mov ds, bx

30907                       00000002            _printf.s	set	2
30908                                             ; get LFB address from PCI
30909                                             ; in - ax: PCI device vendor
30910                                             ; out - ax: LFB address (high 16 bit)
30911                                             ;; NOTE - may be called in protected mode
30912                       0000802D            _pci_get_lfb_addr:
30913 802D           53                           push bx
30914 802E           51                           push cx
30915 802F           52                           push dx
30916 8030     66    50                           push eax
30917 8032           89C3                           mov bx, ax
30918 8034           31C9                           xor cx, cx
30919 8036           B2                     00      mov dl, #0x00
30920 8038           E8         003D                call pci_read_reg
30921 803B           3D                   FFFF      cmp ax, #0xffff
30922 803E           74           12                jz pci_get_lfb_addr_fail
30923                       00008040             pci_get_lfb_addr_next_dev:
30924 8040           B2                     00      mov dl, #0x00
30925 8042           E8         0033                call pci_read_reg
30926 8045           39D8                           cmp ax, bx ;; check vendor
30927 8047           74           0D                jz pci_get_lfb_addr_found
30928 8049           83C1                   08      add cx, #0x8
30929 804C           81F9                 0200      cmp cx, #0x200 ;; search bus #0 and #1
30930 8050           72           EE                jb pci_get_lfb_addr_next_dev
30931                       00008052             pci_get_lfb_addr_fail:
30932 8052           31D2                           xor dx, dx ;; no LFB
30933 8054           EB           1A                jmp pci_get_lfb_addr_return
30934                       00008056             pci_get_lfb_addr_found:
30935 8056           B2                     10      mov dl, #0x10 ;; I/O space #0
30936 8058           E8         001D                call pci_read_reg
30937 805B           A9                   FFF1      test ax, #0xfff1
30938 805E           74           0A                jz pci_get_lfb_addr_success
30939 8060           B2                     14      mov dl, #0x14 ;; I/O space #1
30940 8062           E8         0013                call pci_read_reg
30941 8065           A9                   FFF1      test ax, #0xfff1
30942 8068           75           E8                jnz pci_get_lfb_addr_fail
30943                       0000806A             pci_get_lfb_addr_success:
30944 806A     66    C1E8                   10      shr eax, #16
30945 806E           89C2                           mov dx, ax ;; LFB address
30946                       00008070             pci_get_lfb_addr_return:
30947 8070     66    58                           pop eax
30948 8072           89D0                         mov ax, dx
30949 8074           5A                           pop dx
30950 8075           59                           pop cx
30951 8076           5B                           pop bx
30952 8077           C3                           ret
30953                                             ; read PCI register
30954                                             ; in - cx: device/function
30955                                             ; in - dl: register
30956                                             ; out - eax: value
30957                       00008078            pci_read_reg:
